Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.17,0:00:06.90,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, there was a young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.57,0:00:15.40,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The young woman was to marry a groom chosen by her\Nparents, and not her sweetheart, whom she loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.24,0:00:25.59,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew that her groom loved her very much, but did her\Nsweetheart care for her even more than that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.59,0:00:28.35,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,The young woman wasn't certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:38.60,Narrator,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, after wavering between the two of them, the young woman even became unsure which one of them she really loved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:34.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In searching for a way to return Mytho to the story,\NI just took to hand whatever books struck me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:38.19,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Forgotten Story"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.92,0:02:39.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So why do I choose only books whose endings are missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.82,0:02:40.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.56,0:02:45.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What meaning is there to these torn up books? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.63,0:02:47.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:56.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez, Ahiru, can't you even go a day without\Ngetting yourself put on cleaning duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:57.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, she can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.64,0:02:58.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.44,0:02:59.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, I'm telling you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.08,0:03:00.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.41,0:03:01.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru, you mustn't look right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:06.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:07.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.05,0:03:10.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you do that for, all of a...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:12.88,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Ahiru! There's something you\Nmustn't look at RIGHT THERE, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.76,0:03:15.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.79,0:03:16.12,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.13,0:03:21.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He smiled!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.03,0:03:23.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That totally ruins his bad-boy appeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.06,0:03:25.13,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, we need him to become a\Nfull-fledged juvenile delinquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.13,0:03:28.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this woman who can take the bite out of Fakir-sama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,An older-woman lover has made her appearance, huh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.71,0:03:33.34,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,We still don't know that she's his lover!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.67,0:03:35.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, you should have unreasonable hopes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.78,0:03:36.51,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should make sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.74,0:03:37.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Be brave!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.98,0:03:40.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.52,0:03:43.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Fakir! Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:46.29,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a friend of Fakir's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.29,0:03:47.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's calling her a "friend" right off the bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.42,0:03:48.79,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:50.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about the unfazed confidence of the adult woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.79,0:03:52.56,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if you'd call me a friend or a... a... well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:52.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's like I can see Ahiru's crying face before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sit here any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all just on our way to the ice cream shop. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:03:59.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.97,0:04:02.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, they were just here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an interesting person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:05.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Raetsel. What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.67,0:04:06.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Ahiru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.91,0:04:11.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru-san, we're going to Fakir's house now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:12.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come along with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.38,0:04:12.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.85,0:04:13.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.38,0:04:14.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:15.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.29,0:04:21.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you found out where I was.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.79,0:04:24.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't hide anything from me, Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In our house there's still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:29.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.53,0:04:32.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a long time, hasn't it Karon?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:33.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can come in, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:36.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.17,0:04:39.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you go well together with zura?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.11,0:04:39.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new lovey-dovey zura!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.51,0:04:43.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Karon, this isn't your...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I've seen you since Mytho\Nand I entered Gold Crown Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:51.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I was really lonely then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.05,0:04:51.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:56.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right, I'm like an older sister to Fakir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.59,0:04:57.49,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Older sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, no, I wasn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:05.43,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since my parents died and I was taken in by Karon,\Nshe's been like a surrogate mother to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.10,0:05:08.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is older sister different from lovey-dovey zura?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.44,0:05:10.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then is Raetsel lovey-dovey with Kar...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.77,0:05:12.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Uzura!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.51,Notes,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey! Lovey-dovey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.14,0:05:14.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,How flattering. Do we look like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:18.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't tease adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.81,0:05:20.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to treat me like a child, as always?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.22,0:05:24.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at an age where it wouldn't be odd\Nif I married somebody, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.39,0:05:28.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,To me, you haven't changed one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like when you were romping\Naround with Fakir and Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.76,0:05:33.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, where is Mytho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:36.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, he's at school. He's\Ncompletely wrapped up in his dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:40.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But you always used to be with him,\Nsaying, "I'll protect Mytho!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:42.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I WILL protect him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're staying the night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.11,0:05:46.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's okay. I plan to stay at the water mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:48.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll walk you there, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:53.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, but I think I'd like to take\Na little walk with Ahiru-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.82,0:05:54.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:56.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a tiny bit jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:57.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:59.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir with a girl as cute as you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:01.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no, I'm not cute at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:06.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm always fighting with Fakir, actually\Nsometimes I just can't STAND him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:11.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's thanks to you that Fakir has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:17.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, is Fakir writing stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.71,0:06:19.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stories?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:25.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The stories that boy wrote sometimes came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:29.08,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Stories came true?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.08,0:06:33.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He loved to write stories from the\Ntime when he was very small.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.02,0:06:40.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,They were just silly little stories, but\Nsometimes parts of them came true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:46.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But after he came to Karon's house,\Nhe completely stopped writing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.64,0:06:48.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.84,0:06:53.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I've said a little too much. I wonder if Fakir will scold me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:58.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,To think Fakir wrote stories... And they came true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:04.34,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can do that... maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.76,0:07:10.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm sorry! I just remembered something I have to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:13.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, it was fun talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:15.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.70,0:07:19.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the one who's changed the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.57,0:07:21.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.54,0:07:24.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.21,0:07:28.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I protect him? Who do I fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:32.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me, Fakir, my heart is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.58,0:07:35.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In the story, you're no longer needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:37.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.19,0:07:43.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The story is moving... Whether I'm here or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But all I have... is a sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:55.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Mytho with this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.24,0:07:57.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.57,0:08:03.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir, I heard from Raetsel-san that\Nthe stories you write come true!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:06.21,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.21,0:08:10.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do have that power, then if you\Nwrite a story where Mytho is saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.25,0:08:12.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:14.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:15.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.16,0:08:20.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, I heard the stories you wrote\Nwhen you were little came true...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:21.66,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.66,0:08:23.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.06,0:08:24.33,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.63,0:08:28.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, shut up? Why\Nare you talking to me that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.27,0:08:33.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could help Mytho by myself, I wouldn't ask you to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.68,0:08:36.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I can't do anything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.34,0:08:36.84,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:41.54,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Mytho as a knight. I won't take orders from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:42.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fak...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:45.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir, why?! Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.99,0:08:51.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir! Come on, Fakir! If you can help\NMytho, then why won't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:55.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that attitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:59.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We were waiting for you so we'd be ready\Nwhenever you came home crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:01.57,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what happened with Fakir-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:02.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that Fakir anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:04.87,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good! Get angry and cry as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.24,0:09:07.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll give you lots of comfort!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:09.81,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought we'd be able to help Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:11.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lately it's like Mytho-sama is a totally different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.66,0:09:23.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's scary somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.96,0:09:25.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He makes the hairs on the back of my neck stand up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.74,0:09:36.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:40.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho... I'm jealous of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.11,0:09:42.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.04,0:09:43.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could live without changing, like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.98,0:09:45.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.15,0:09:48.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm different than I was before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.42,0:09:51.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I've gotten my heart back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:55.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can even accept your love for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.06,0:10:02.13,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that makes me happy. Maybe I'll call off the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:03.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:08.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Mytho-san. Which means the girl is Rue-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.67,0:10:11.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of them are getting married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:14.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that right, getting married...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:16.11,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Students of mine are getting married before me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.11,0:10:19.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no happier thing for a teacher than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.88,0:10:21.22,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.22,0:10:22.38,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:25.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't look very happy. Could it be you're wavering?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.59,0:10:29.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not. What I said before was a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.29,0:10:33.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hans will love me from the bottom of his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.63,0:10:36.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,With him, I'm sure I can be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:40.16,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't lie to your own feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.77,0:10:43.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a pure and beautiful heart, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.34,0:10:46.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going now, Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.51,0:10:53.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to love me. Sacrifice your life and love me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:11:01.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do as Father says, someday he'll be my prince alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:03.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.23,0:11:09.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The fight between the prince and the raven is being\Nfought with fiercer and fiercer desperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.40,0:11:13.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,In a place where no one can see it, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.91,0:11:27.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's definitely toying with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:33.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, a Fakir played thoroughly by an adult woman\Nand then tossed away like a tattered dishrag!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:35.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, how wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.12,0:11:39.06,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love for him to keep on like this and\Nbecome more and more of a delinquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.36,0:11:39.62,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir said he'd protect Mytho, so why?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:44.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect Mytho as a knight. I won't take orders from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.33,0:11:48.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was starting to look like we'd\Nbe able to work together too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:52.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want things to stay like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.91,0:11:53.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.71,0:11:55.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait, where are you going, Ahiru?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.01,0:11:59.84,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for the second round, right?\NOh, Ahiru, you do so love battles!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.28,0:12:02.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, so Fakir said that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.18,0:12:08.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to help someone, and he's someone\Nimportant to Fakir too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.46,0:12:13.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought if Fakir wrote a story,\Nmaybe we could help him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.83,0:12:14.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.36,0:12:17.50,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is because I said something I shouldn't have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.00,0:12:22.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru-san, will you pretend you\Nnever heard what I said before?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.44,0:12:25.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? But if that person is saved, Fakir will be happy too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.41,0:12:28.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But in exchange, Fakir will be hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.64,0:12:29.61,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:34.25,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, a lot of crows once\Nshowed up in Gold Crown Town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.31,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Crows?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.82,0:12:39.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The crows attacked the townspeople indiscriminately.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.05,0:12:43.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir was a child, but he must have\Nwanted to do something to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.33,0:12:48.69,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He wrote a story where he became\Na hero and defeated the crows.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.70,0:12:55.03,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And then just like Fakir had written,\Nthe crows came and attacked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.64,0:12:59.30,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But the ending was different than his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.64,0:13:05.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Afterwards, it was as if he'd sealed those memories away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.41,0:13:07.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He never talked about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:10.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And he stopped writing stories too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.69,0:13:18.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that Fakir had something\Nlike that happen to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.46,0:13:20.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He must still be unable to recover from it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:25.90,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru-san, please give Fakir space.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.17,0:13:29.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I came to get you, Raetsel...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.78,0:13:36.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,My bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.64,0:13:40.27,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey! Lovey-dovey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahiru, what's wrong zura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.52,0:13:46.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the worst. What should I say to Fakir?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:49.42,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to say something to Fakir zura?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.99,0:13:52.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of crows zura!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:54.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The water mill.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.66,0:13:57.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could Mytho be doing to Raetsel-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.88,0:14:16.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel, I'll give you a love with no wavering.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:20.02,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll love only me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:24.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:31.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Raetsel, and give your beautiful heart to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:35.09,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Mytho's bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.90,0:14:37.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.91,0:14:40.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.60,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Princess Tutu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:48.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Dance with me, Raetsel-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.65,0:14:50.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Princess Tutu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:54.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do have that power, then if you\Nwrite a story where Mytho is saved...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this awful feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.53,0:15:02.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,The power to make stories come true?\NA power like that, in me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:05.83,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovey-dovey, lovey-dovey, lovey-dovey...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.50,0:15:04.80,Person2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:07.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.24,0:15:10.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that Mytho is lovey-dovey with Raetsel-san zura?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.41,0:15:19.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a lovely wedding dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.28,0:15:22.58,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You have someone you're engaged to, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.58,0:15:23.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.82,0:15:29.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Karon knows how I feel, but he didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.36,0:15:30.15,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.56,0:15:34.96,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But Hans... He tells me of his love.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:37.70,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks at only me, and holds me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:43.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I love him too. But no matter what I do,\NI see Karon's face in my mind!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.47,0:15:46.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're suffering because you're wavering between two loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you love me, your wavering will disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.78,0:15:51.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't go over there. What's wrong with wavering?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:54.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's something you feel because you truly love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.98,0:15:58.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I may still love Karon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.35,0:16:02.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,When I think that, being with him is so hard and so painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:04.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Karon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to waver anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.57,0:16:13.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! If you love only me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.94,0:16:15.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I love only Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.77,0:16:18.71,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,No! That's a mistake, Raetsel-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.71,0:16:21.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just forget everything else, and love only me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.88,0:16:25.01,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of those are your true heart, Raetsel-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:28.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But is what you're trying to get right now your true feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,"True" and "false" have nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:32.95,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,People just love others because they want to be loved!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.29,0:16:35.86,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,So she wavers because she wonders which one will love her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.86,0:16:39.33,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That pain is how you really feel! So wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.33,0:16:42.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be happy with the one you love most, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.47,0:16:51.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I weighed their loves against each other\Nfor the sake of my own happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:56.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,To escape from the pain of my wavering, I set\Nout to get Fakir to write a story about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.28,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I knew it would hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.28,0:17:01.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a horrible woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:03.92,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone wants to be loved by the people they love.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not bad to feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's painful to waver between two loves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.12,0:17:13.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But even if you run away from that, you\Nwon't be able to escape the pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.63,0:17:20.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You should just love me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.00,0:17:22.26,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.80,0:17:26.24,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho! I won't allow you to hurt Raetsel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:29.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.56,0:17:44.62,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! The two of you fighting is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.97,0:17:58.93,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho, do you feel nothing? Using even Raetsel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.67,0:18:02.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried to save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:14.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save her"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.99,0:18:16.52,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just prattle what's convenient for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What can YOU do, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.03,0:18:21.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A knight who couldn't even die shouldn't talk so big!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.80,0:18:27.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,How pathetic you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:32.73,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,How long do you mean to go on shaming\Nyourself wielding your play sword?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.27,0:18:34.87,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.98,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You know you can't lay a finger on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.98,0:18:40.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword isn't for slaying you with!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.72,0:18:44.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up! Remember your true self!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.89,0:18:46.91,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.69,0:18:53.68,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.40,0:18:58.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! SHUT UP!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.04,0:19:05.20,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:16.45,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it. Don't hurt Fakir, you raven!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.45,0:19:17.35,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:23.19,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! Don't... Don't come near me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:27.79,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.50,0:19:32.57,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel! Raetsel...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.57,0:19:36.00,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir, I'm sorry. I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought only of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.64,0:19:42.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I forgot everything but my desire to escape my pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.84,0:19:45.04,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I did something to hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.65,0:19:46.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.21,0:19:51.12,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. It's not your fault, Raetsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.42,0:19:58.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel-san was suffering so much, but she told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.13,0:20:01.53,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,She told me to give you space.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.53,0:20:07.63,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel-san didn't want to hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.47,0:20:09.56,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.17,0:20:11.80,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of Raetsel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:14.67,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.45,0:20:21.18,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't want to hurt you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:27.72,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hurt Fakir, you raven!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:32.89,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,If I could help Mytho by myself, I wouldn't ask you to do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.89,0:20:35.66,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, I can't do anything, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.10,0:20:39.07,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What I can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.14,0:20:47.51,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.85,0:20:57.88,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:20:59.78,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:03.05,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.39,0:21:05.48,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.66,0:21:11.46,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, did you write a story for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:16.40,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Karon, I'm going to marry Hans.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.40,0:21:17.44,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:19.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.94,0:21:20.64,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Raetsel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.64,0:21:25.55,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, I think I wanted to say a proper goodbye to Karon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.55,0:21:29.41,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll take this. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.32,0:21:33.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Your story didn't come true, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.59,0:21:35.76,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:36.82,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.82,0:21:39.39,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll try writing one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.39,0:21:40.36,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.23,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,A story about Mytho.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:47.74,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's dangerous. That power is truly dangerous, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:50.37,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You couldn't even completely become a knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.81,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you really be able to master it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.81,0:21:54.14,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.93,0:23:29.77,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,They took out the endings to stop the\Nstories from becoming real?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.77,0:23:30.47,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,He's awakened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:31.17,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.17,0:23:33.97,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he's gained the knowledge, but that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:36.94,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a direct descendant of Drosselmeyer's,\Nand this is your level?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.94,0:23:37.75,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.75,0:23:39.85,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,You hesitated to take my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.85,0:23:42.32,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Mytho was always kind to Rue-chan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:44.59,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,To those who accept everything, happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.59,0:23:46.65,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,To those who resist everything, glory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.65,0:23:48.99,Person1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fakir, please wake up.
